➜福州为新福州人举行中式集体婚礼
http://www.sohu.com/a/429201105_123753	27420
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201103/69592112112048fcbe30b890038994ea.jpeg" /></p>
<p>吕明　摄</p>
